### Jimudu Wallet API Testing Script
### Based on comprehensive Jimudu Wallet vision document

### Authentication Endpoints
### Test user registration with Jimudu Wallet branding
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "254712345678",
  "fullName": "Amara Kariuki",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "email": "amara.kariuki@jimudu.com"
}

### Test user login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "254712345678",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

### Test OTP verification
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "phoneNumber": "254712345678",
  "otpCode": "123456"
}

### Discipline Bucket Endpoints
### Get all discipline buckets for user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/discipline/buckets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Set daily allowance - Core Jimudu Wallet feature
POST http://localhost:8080/api/discipline/daily-allowance
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "dailyAmount": 600,
  "emergencySavingsTarget": 3000,
  "mmfSweepEnabled": true,
  "weeklyAllowance": 4200,
  "monthlyAllowance": 18000
}

### Get financial health score - Key differentiator
GET http://localhost:8080/api/discipline/health-score
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get discipline streaks and analytics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/discipline/streaks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reallocate funds between buckets
POST http://localhost:8080/api/discipline/reallocate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "fromBucket": "EMERGENCY_SAVINGS",
  "toBucket": "SPENDING_WALLET",
  "amount": 500,
  "reason": "Emergency expense"
}

### Transaction Endpoints
### Deposit money with M-Pesa integration
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transactions/deposit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 5000,
  "phoneNumber": "254712345678",
  "source": "M-PESA",
  "reference": "Salary deposit"
}

### Withdraw from spending wallet with limits
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transactions/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "bucketType": "SPENDING_WALLET",
  "amount": 150,
  "recipientPhoneNumber": "254712345679",
  "reference": "Grocery shopping"
}

### Get transaction history with behavioral insights
GET http://localhost:8080/api/transactions?page=0&size=20&includeBehavioral=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### MMF Growth Bucket Endpoints
### Get MMF investment details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mmf/investments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Trigger MMF sweep - Core wealth building feature
POST http://localhost:8080/api/mmf/sweep
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 450,
  "autoSweep": true
}

### Get MMF yield history
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mmf/yield-history?period=monthly
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Overdraft Facility Endpoints
### Get overdraft facility details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/overdraft/facility
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Apply for behavior-linked overdraft
POST http://localhost:8080/api/overdraft/apply
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "requestedAmount": 2000,
  "purpose": "Emergency expense",
  "repaymentPlan": "Next salary"
}

### Get overdraft pricing with transparency
GET http://localhost:8080/api/overdraft/pricing?amount=1000&disciplineScore=87
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Transparency Engine Endpoints
### Get fee breakdown for transaction - Key trust builder
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transparency/fee-breakdown
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "transactionType": "OVERDRAFT",
  "principalAmount": 1000,
  "duration": "30_days",
  "disciplineScore": 87
}

### Get complete cost breakdown
GET http://localhost:8080/api/transparency/cost-breakdown?transactionId=12345
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Financial Nudges Endpoints
### Get personalized financial nudges
GET http://localhost:8080/api/nudges/personalized
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get spending insights and recommendations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/nudges/spending-insights
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Mark nudge as acted upon
POST http://localhost:8080/api/nudges/{{nudgeId}}/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "ACCEPTED",
  "feedback": "Helpful recommendation"
}

### Analytics and Reporting Endpoints
### Get user financial wellness metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/analytics/wellness-metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get spending pattern analysis
GET http://localhost:8080/api/analytics/spending-patterns?period=30_days
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get emergency savings progress
GET http://localhost:8080/api/analytics/emergency-progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

