### User Profile and Settings
### Get user profile with discipline metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update user preferences
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/preferences
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "dailyAllowanceNotifications": true,
  "mmfSweepEnabled": true,
  "nudgeFrequency": "daily",
  "riskTolerance": "moderate"
}

### Get account settings
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### B2B Partnership Endpoints
### Get partner dashboard (for MFIs, Employers, NGOs)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/partner/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{partner_token}}

### Get behavioral data insights (for partners)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/partner/behavioral-insights?partnerId=mfi001
Authorization: Bearer {{partner_token}}

### Compliance and Reporting
### Get transaction audit trail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/compliance/audit-trail?userId=1&startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Generate regulatory report
POST http://localhost:8080/api/compliance/regulatory-report
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "reportType": "monthly",
  "format": "json"
}

### Health Check
### Basic health check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### Detailed system health
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health/detailed
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
